---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Indian Wedding Catering Vancouver | Halal, Vegetarian, Vegan | Sula Catering"
	description="Award-winning Indian wedding catering in Vancouver since 2010. Sangeet, mehndi, ceremony, and reception menus. Halal-certified, vegetarian, vegan, and Jain options. Custom-built with your chef."
	canonical="/weddings"
	ogImage="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/WEDDING.jpg"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "Service",
			"name": "Indian Wedding Catering Vancouver",
			"provider": { "@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization" },
			"areaServed": ["Vancouver", "Burnaby", "Richmond", "Surrey", "North Vancouver"],
			"serviceType": "Wedding Catering",
			"description": "Custom Indian wedding catering in Vancouver — sangeet, mehndi, ceremony, and reception menus with halal, vegetarian, vegan, and Jain options."
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/WEDDING.jpg');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<p class="gold-label">Wedding Catering</p>
			<h1>Indian Wedding Catering<br/>in <em>Vancouver</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">From sangeet to reception — flawless execution, exquisite presentation, and the warmth of true Indian hospitality.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Wedding Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Tradition Meets Excellence</p>
				<h2>Your Wedding, <em>Our Honour</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p>Sula has catered hundreds of South Asian weddings across the Lower Mainland — from intimate fifty-guest ceremonies to grand five-hundred-plus receptions. Every event is led by a dedicated wedding coordinator and supported by a kitchen team trained in the regional cuisines of India. We understand the rhythm of a wedding day, the importance of timing, and the silent choreography that turns a celebration into a memory.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/weddinf-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Indian wedding catering Vancouver BC" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="alt-row">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/weddin-catering-burnaby-vancouver.webp" alt="Sangeet catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-right">
					<p class="gold-label">Sangeet & Mehndi</p>
					<h2>Live Stations, <em>Lively Nights</em></h2>
					<p>Pani puri at the chaat counter. Dosas crisping at the tava station. Chai pouring from copper urns. Our live cooking stations turn pre-wedding events into immersive experiences your guests will remember long after the henna fades.</p>
					<p>Pair with our chai bar from Sula Café for a complete sensory experience.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="alt-row reverse">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-right">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp" alt="Wedding ceremony lunch catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-left">
					<p class="gold-label">Ceremony Lunches</p>
					<h2>Vegetarian Feasts, <em>Honoured Traditions</em></h2>
					<p>Pure-vegetarian thalis and Jain-friendly buffets prepared in dedicated kitchen areas. Honouring religious traditions has always been at the heart of how we cater — quietly, carefully, without compromise.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="alt-row">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Wedding reception catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-right">
					<p class="gold-label">Reception Dinners</p>
					<h2>The Main Event, <em>Perfectly Plated</em></h2>
					<p>North Indian, South Indian, and Indo-Chinese feasts featuring halal-certified meats, tandoori specialties, and dessert spreads designed to leave a lasting impression. Plated service or buffet — your choice.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="image-banner" style="background-image: url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/WEDDING.jpg');">
		<div class="image-banner-content reveal">
			<h2>Every Detail, <em>Considered</em></h2>
			<p>From dietary needs to dietary dreams — we say yes.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Full-Service Wedding Catering</p>
				<h2 style="font-size:42px;font-weight:400">What's <em style="color:var(--gold)">Included</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="services-grid">
				<div class="service-card reveal">
					<h3>Custom Menus</h3>
					<p>Build your menu with our chef. Vegan, Jain, gluten-friendly, regional preferences welcome.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card reveal delay-100">
					<h3>Dedicated Coordinator</h3>
					<p>One point of contact from your first email to the final cleanup. We handle the timeline.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card reveal delay-200">
					<h3>Live Cooking Stations</h3>
					<p>Chaat counters, dosa stations, tandoori grills. Live cooking turns dinner into theatre.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card reveal delay-300">
					<h3>Setup & Cleanup</h3>
					<p>Buffets, plated service, professional servers. We arrive early and leave the venue spotless.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="testimonial-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">From Our Couples</p>
				<p class="testimonial-quote">We had over 400 guests and Sula handled every single dietary requirement — vegan, Jain, halal, gluten-free. Not one complaint. The chaat station was the talk of the night.</p>
				<p class="testimonial-author">— Aanya & Rohan · Reception, 420 Guests</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Common Questions</p>
				<h2 style="font-size:42px;font-weight:400">Wedding Catering <em style="color:var(--gold)">FAQs</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="faq-list">
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you offer halal meat?</h3><p>Yes — all chicken and lamb dishes are prepared using halal-certified meats sourced from trusted local BC suppliers.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Can you cater pure-vegetarian or Jain weddings?</h3><p>Absolutely. We offer dedicated vegetarian, vegan, and Jain menus prepared in separate kitchen areas to honour traditional dietary requirements.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>What is your minimum guest count?</h3><p>We cater weddings from 50 to 500+ guests. Smaller intimate events are also welcome — please reach out to discuss.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you provide servers and setup?</h3><p>Yes — full-service catering includes setup, professional servers, buffet management, and complete cleanup.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>How far in advance should we book?</h3><p>For peak season weddings (May–October), we recommend booking 6–9 months in advance. Off-season bookings are more flexible.</p></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<p class="gold-label" style="color:var(--gold-light)">Begin the Conversation</p>
			<h2>Let's Plan Your <em>Wedding</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us about your event. We'll respond within 24 hours with a custom menu and quote.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Wedding Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
